OL,3,C'The drones are like bees': Ukrainian
OL,4,Csoldiers speak from the frontline
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent John Ray sent
OL,7,Fthis eyewitness report from the
OL,8,Ffrontline with Ukrainian forces as
OL,9,Fthey try to repel a fresh offensive by
OL,10,Finvading Russians
OL,12,FOleg is a long way from home. A
OL,13,Fthousand kilometres,
OL,15,FHe's an architect by profession, from
OL,16,FLviv, on the western edge of his
OL,17,Fcountry.
OL,19,FBut we meet him - and his exhausted
OL,20,Fplatoon - close to the front line in
OL,21,Fthe far northeast.
