OL,3,C'The drones are like bees': Ukrainian
OL,4,Csoldiers speak from the frontline
OL,6,F"They (the Russians) are striking
OL,7,Feverything. Everything they can," he
OL,8,Ftells us.
OL,10,FHis team are taking a break after five
OL,11,Fintense days of fighting. Soon they'll
OL,12,Fbe back in action.
OL,14,F"It's very difficult. Physically and
OL,15,Femotionally. The drones are like bees.
OL,16,FAll you here is buzzing. It's like
OL,17,Frain."
