OL,3,C'The drones are like bees': Ukrainian
OL,4,Csoldiers speak from the frontline
OL,6,FWe're heading towards Vovchansk, the
OL,7,FUkrainian town close to the border
OL,8,Fthat is now a front line after the
OL,9,Frecent Russian incursion.
OL,11,FAnother soldier tells us there's
OL,12,Flittle left of the town but its name.
OL,14,FThese are anxious times for Ukraine,
OL,15,Fand for our hosts, the 57th Brigade.
OL,17,FAs we arrive at their artillery
OL,18,Fposition, we're greeted by machine gun
OL,19,Ffire.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/7
