OL,3,C'The drones are like bees': Ukrainian
OL,4,Csoldiers speak from the frontline
OL,6,FThey're hunting yet another drone
OL,7,Fthat's been spotted overhead.
OL,9,FCompared to my last visit to the
OL,10,Ffrontline, there's an increase in the
OL,11,Fscale and intensity of drone attacks.
OL,13,FWant a quick and expert briefing on
OL,14,Fthe biggest news stories? Listen to
OL,15,Four latest podcasts to find out What
OL,16,FYou Need To Know...
OL,18,FThe unit now has a drone marksman. His
OL,19,Ffingers drum across his rifle. He is
OL,20,Fyet to shoot one down.
