OL,3,C'The drones are like bees': Ukrainian
OL,4,Csoldiers speak from the frontline
OL,6,FThey, and we, will spend many of the
OL,7,Fcoming hours together hiding in
OL,8,Fbunkers and tree lines.
OL,10,FOne of the self-propelled guns has
OL,11,Fbroken down. It won't fire today.
OL,13,FThey say they have enough ammunition,
OL,14,Fbut there is no other sign of the
OL,15,Flatest American military aid package
OL,16,Fmaking much impact.
OL,18,FThe Russians out-gun, and crucially,
OL,19,Fout-number the Ukrainian forces here.
