OL,3,C'The drones are like bees': Ukrainian
OL,4,Csoldiers speak from the frontline
OL,6,FDmytro, a local commander, tells us
OL,7,Fhis unit has been moved here to shore
OL,8,Fup defences. There's a danger that
OL,9,Fleaves the line elsewhere much thinner.
OL,11,F''I really worry about that. There are
OL,12,Fa lot of Russians. We need more of
OL,13,Feverything. The front line was already
OL,14,Fvery long. Now it's even longer.''
OL,16,FThe mood is anxious. The future
OL,17,Funcertain. And with Russian forces
OL,18,Fmassing elsewhere along the border,
OL,19,Fthese troops are prepared for a long
OL,20,Fand difficult summer ahead.
